OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowery rain
OL,6,Fgradually clearing eastwards, allowing
OL,7,Fsome late evening sunshine in parts of
OL,8,FDevon and Cornwall. Largely dry
OL,9,Fovernight with clear periods, most
OL,10,Fprolonged in eastern counties. Winds
OL,11,Feasing with fog patches forming
OL,12,Finland. Frost possible in prone rural
OL,13,Fspots.
OL,14,
OL,15,CSaturday:FGenerally fine with sunny
OL,16,Fspells, these most prevalent first
OL,17,Fthing. Showers possible in
OL,18,FGloucestershire and Wiltshire later. A
OL,19,Ffresher feeling day despite light
OL,20,Fwinds, but pleasantly warm in the
OL,21,Fsunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
